highlights.text: “Passa o Teu Bigode” by Lukão Mec, Dj Adah, and Lado Sul is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #175.
“Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 888 days straight.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #12.
“Coisas Que Eu Sei” by Felipe Amorim is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 41 spots at #136.
